  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK206">
<l>tīppāla tāṉpiṟarkaṭ ceyyaṟka nōyppāla</l>
<l>taṉṉai yaṭalvēṇṭā tāṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Let him not do evil to others who desires not that sorrows should pursue him.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
